<h3>What is a DAO?</h3>

  <p><strong>DAOs (Decentralized Autonomous Organizations</strong>) are online communities where decisions are made through community votes. Basic criteria for participation is based on ownership of tokens or NFTs. Some DAOs enable direct voting on proposals, while others enable token holders to delegate their votes to a trusted DAO representative.</p>

